\mt1 Rut
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n eghaghanim an eghaghanir bar aghuim. Gumazir dapanibar dughiam…®n an oto. Rut a Moapian amizim, a Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir mam…®n ikia aning Moap…®n nguazim…®n iti. Ez…® an pam aremez…®, a uan asamir amebam geghufi. Egha g…®n aning uamategha Judian nguazim…®n ghu. Rut uaghan Israelian God…®n apengan iti. A g…®n gumazir igharazim…®n ikia atrivim Devit…®n inaghamim…®n oto. Atrivim Devit a Israelian atrivir aghuir faragha zuim.
\ip N…® ak…®nafarir kam d…®pon…®va, amizir kam gifuegham, a faragha God g…®fozir puvat…®gha arazir kurabagh ami. Dat…®r…®gh…®n a uan navim isa Israelian God gan…®ngi. Egha uaghan uan navim isa uan asamir amebam gan…®ngi. Rut amizir arazir aghuir kam, a God Israelia gan…®ngizir arazim ko magh ghu, ‚ÄúIa uan navir averiabar aven bar God gifongegh,‚Äù egh, ‚ÄúIgharaz darazi sara ifongegh.‚Äù Ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n en akakasi, gumazamizir God…®n saghon itiba uaghan God…®n bizir aghuariba iniva an adarazir tong…®n ikiam. Egh arazir kam…®n, God…®n saghon itir gumazir vam…®ran arazim Israel…®n aven tir marazigh afiragham.
\c 1
\ms1 Dughiar kuram Naomi bato
\mr (Sapta 1)
\s1 Naomin adarazi kantri Moap…®n areme
\p 
\v 1 Bar fom…®ra gumazir dapanir maba kantri Israel…®n garir dughiam, dagheba puvat…®zir dughiam oto. Ez…® Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n gumazir mam, Betlehem Judian Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam. Dughiar kam…®n Israel…®n dagheba puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…® gumazir kam uan amuim ko otarimning inigha azenir mabar kantri Moap…®n ikiasa ghu.
\v 2 Gumazim…®n ziam Elimelek, ez…® an amuim…®n ziam Naomi, ez…® an otarimning…®n ziamning Malon ko Kilion, me Efratan dakozim…®n adarasi. Egha me Betlehem…®n nguibar Judian nguazim…®n aven itim…®n ikegha ghua Moap…®n apera.
\v 3 Egha g…®n Naomin pam Elimelek aremez…®, a uan otarimning ko me uarira iti.
\v 4-5 Ez…® g…®n an otarimning Moapian amizimning…®n iti. Aning…®n ziamning Orpa ko Rut. Ez…® me 10plan azenibar ikia ghua Malon ko Kilion areme. An pam ko otarimning, me bar ariaghire, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Naomi bar uab…®ra iti.
\s1 Rut arazir aghuim…®n Naomi gami
\p 
\v 6 Egha Naomi Moap…®n ikia orazi Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan adarazi deragha me gamua dagheba me gan…®di. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan asamir guivimning ko d…®kavigha ua Judan nguazim…®n mangasa.
\v 7 Egha Naomi uan asamir guivimning ko d…®kavigha ua Judan nguazim…®n mangasa tuavim…®n zui.
\p 
\v 8 Egha me ghua Naomi kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…® uan amebamning ko ik…®. Gua arazir bar aghuibar na gamua, egha uaghan par aremezimning saram ami. Kamagh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uaghan guan apangkuvigh arazir aghuaribar gua damuam.
\v 9 Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God guan akurvagh arazir aghuim gua damut…®, gua ua patamning inigh derav…®ra ik…®.‚Äù
\p Egha aning…®n torez…® aning puv…®ram azi.
\v 10 Ez…® an asamir guivimning a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Ga uaghan mang…® n…® ko n…®n adarazi ko ikiasa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Naomi kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivimning, gua uamategh mang…®. Gua tizim bagh nan g…®n mangasa? K…® manmagh…®n otaritamning bateght…® gua uam aning…®n ikiam?
\v 12 Nan guivimning, gua uamatengegh uan nguibamning…®n mang…®. Gua fo, k…® bar ghurigha g…®vagha, ua patam…®n ikian ibura. Tuaviba bar puvat…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®mangan patam…®n ik…® egh borir tamning bateght…®,
\v 13 gua aning m…®zuamigh egh aning…®n ikiam? Ti puvat…®gham. Egh gua ua odiarimning…®n ik…®va aning m…®zuam ikiam? Ti puvat…®gham, nan guivimning. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God os…®mt…®zim na gan…®ngi! Kamagh…®n, nan os…®mt…®zir nan navim…®n itim mati dagher m…®sozim k…® anepima a nan akam m…®sosi. Ez…® nan os…®mt…®zir kam, guan os…®mt…®zimning gafira.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Rut ko Orpa, ua puv…®ram azi. Aning aziava Orpa uan asamir amebam…®n toregha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® zui.‚Äù Ez…® Rut Naomin suiragha gavgavigha mangan aghua.
\v 15 Ez…® Naomi Rut m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gan, n…®n penem zui, a uan gumazamiziba ko uan aseba bagha zui. N…® an g…®n mang…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:15 \ft Kantri Moap…®n gumazamiziba, me aser av…®ribar ziaba fe, da aseba ko marvir guaba ko dag…®aba ko bizir av…®rir igharaziba uakan.\f*
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Rut 2:11-12; 2 Atriviba 2:2-6\x*Ez…® Rut kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n g…®n mang…®s…®, n…® nan anogoroghan mark…®. Egh uamategh mang…®s…® na m…®k…®man mark…®. Danganir n…® mangamim, k…® uaghan an mangam. Egh danganir n…® ikiamim k…® uaghan an ikiam. Ez…® n…®n adarasi, me uaghan nan adarasi, ez…® n…®n God, a uaghan nan God.
\v 17 Eght…® danganir n…® managh ik…®va oveghamim, k…® uaghan an ik…®va ovegham. Eght…® me danganir kam…®n narafagham. Bizitam ga abighan kogham, ovevemra ga abigham. Puvat…®ght…®ma Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir bar kuratam…®n na damika.‚Äù
\v 18 Ez…® Naomi garima, Rut an g…®n mangasa n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uam a m…®geir puvat…®.
\v 19 Egha aning ghua Betlehem…®n oto.
\s1 Naomi os…®mt…®zir ekiam ikia ua Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n ize
\p Naomi ko Rut ghua Betlehem…®n otoz…®, nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar, d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha Betlehem…®n amiziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar ti Naomi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Naomi ghaze, ‚ÄúIa ‚ÄòNaomi,‚Äô na dar…®ghan mark…®. Ziar kam kamak…®n, amizir navir aghuim itim. Puvat…®. God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim navir os…®mt…®zim na gan…®ngi. Ez…® ia ‚ÄòMara,‚Äô na dar…®gh, ziar kam kamak…®n, amizir navir kuram itim, mati dagher m…®sozim pamten an akam m…®sosi.
\v 21 K…® nguibar kam ataghizir dughiam, k…® bizir bar av…®rim iti, mati m…®nem biziba a giz…®fa. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua na inigha izezir dughiam…®n k…® biziba bar puvat…®, m…®ner m…®sevir k…®nim, biziba an aven itir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®zazim na gan…®ngi. God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim os…®mt…®zir av…®rav…®rim na gat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Naomi na dar…®ghan mark…®!‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Naomi ko an asamir guivim Rut, a Moap…®n amizim, aning Betlehem…®n izima, dughiar bali aghoramim oto.\f + \fr 1:22 \ft Bali a raiz…®n m…®n garir daghem. Me an ov…®zibav sozima, da menmeniar k…®nibar otifi. Ez…® me da isa bretbagh ami.\f*
\c 2
\ms1 Rut Boas…®n azenim…®n dagheba buri
\mr (Sapta 2)
\s1 Rut mang…® dagheba buriasa
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Boas a gumazir aruar bizir av…®riba itir mam, a Naomin par ovengezim Elimelek…®n adarazir mav.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Ofa Gami 19:9-10; God…®n Araziba 24:19\x*Ez…® Rut kamagh…®n Naomi m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan amamangat…®ght…®, k…® azenibar mang…® balin ov…®zibagh eghuvam. Ingangarir gumaziba dar akora da ar…®ki. Egh me ifueght…®, k…® men g…®n mang…®va, da inigh izam.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Naomi kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivim, a dera, n…® mang…®.‚Äù
\v 3 Ez…® Rut azenibar ghua ingangarir gumazibar g…®n ghua balin ov…®ziba izi. Dughiar kam Rut a fozir puvat…®, kar Boas…®n azeniba, a Elimelek…®n adarazir mav…®ra.
\s1 Boas arazir aghuim…®n Rut gami
\p 
\v 4 Dughiar kamra Boas Betlehem ategha iza uan ingangarir gumaziba batogha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ia ko iti.‚Äù Ez…® me a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God deragh n…® damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Boas iza men garir gumazir dapanim…®n azara, ‚ÄúAmizir munam, a ik…®zir manam…®n amizim?‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba ghaze, ‚ÄúKar Moapian amizim a Naomi ko kantri Moap…®n ikegha ize.
\v 7 A ingangarir gumazibar g…®n mang…® balin ik…®zir me ikegha g…®vaziba, an adar tigh…®n mang…® balin ov…®ziba iniasa, nan azai. A m…®zaraghara ingara ghua dat…®r…®gh…®n. A dughiar otevimra avughsasa ghua averpenim…®n aperagha avughsi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Boas kamagh…®n Rut m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivim, n…® nan azenim…®n kagh…®ra ik…®, egh ua bagh balin ov…®zibagh eghuv. Gumazir igharazitam…®n azenim…®n mangan mark…®. N…® nan ingangarir amiziba ko kagh…®ra ik…®.
\v 9 N…® ingangarir amizibar gan, me ingara ghua managh tu n…® merara g…®n mang…®. K…® n…® bagha ingangarir gumaziba akar gavgavim me gan…®ngi. Me arazir kuratam n…® damighan kogham. Kuarim n…®n p…®rt…®, n…® mang…® m…®ner ekiar ingangarir gumaziba d…®paba tuiziba, dar d…®patam amegh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Rut irava nguazim…®n fuagha, uan guam nguazim m…®tuagha ir…®ghav ikia kamagh…®n Boas m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kantrin igharazim…®n amizim. Ez…® n…® manmagh…®n nan gara na g…®fogha derav…®ra na gami?‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Boas kamagh…®n a ikara, ‚ÄúK…® oregha fo, fom…®ra n…®n pam aremezir dughiam…®n, n…® arazir aghuibar uan asamir amebam gamua iza dat…®r…®k…®n. K…® fo, n…® uan amebam ko afeziam ko uan nguibam ategha iza gumazamizir n…® fom…®ra fozir puvat…®ziba ko iti.
\v 12 N…® arazir aghuim gamizir bizim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® ikaragh ivezir aghuim n…® dan…®ng. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God n…® geghuv n…® avaragh n…®n ganasa n…® ifonge, kamaghsua n…® a bagha ize. Eght…® a deraghv…®ra n…® damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Rut kamagh…®n Boas m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan ekiam, k…® n…®n damazim…®n derav…®ram oto. K…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® fo, k…® tong n…®n ingangarir amizibar m…®n itir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® arazir aghuaribar na gamua, n…®m…®ra na m…®geima nan navim bar dera.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® damamin dughiam, Boas kamagh…®n Rut m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…® bret tam inigh wain…®n d…®par m…®sozim darugh anemegh.‚Äù Ez…® Rut ingangarir gumaziba ko aperaz…®, Boas balin tuezir maba a gan…®ngi. Ez…® an apa ghua bar iz…®vaz…® dar naba iti.
