\v 19 Ez…® Naomi Rut…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® managh balin kaba ini? Egha n…® tinan azenim…®n ingari? K…® ghaze, gumazir derav…®ra n…® gamim, God, n…® derav…®ram a damu.‚Äù Ez…® Rut kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an azenim…®n ingarizim, an ziam Boas.‚Äù
