\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Ofa Gami 25:25\x*Ez…® Naomi kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God deragh gumazir kam damu. A uan m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n g…®n ghuava ariaghireziba ko angam…®ra itiba, men apangkuva arazir aghuibar me gami.‚Äù
\p Egha a ua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam e ko ik…®zir vam…®ra, egha en akurvazir gumazim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Rut ua kamagh…®n Naomi m…®gei, ‚ÄúBoas uaghan na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòK…® an ingangarir amiziba ko ingarv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® ingangarim g…®vagham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Naomi kamagh…®n uan asamim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra n…® gumazir igharazim…®n azenim…®n ingart…® me paz…® n…® damuam. Kamagh…®n deragham n…® Boas…®n ingangarir amiziba ko ingar.‚Äù
