\v 23 Ez…® Rut Boas…®n ingangarir amiziba ko ingangarim gamua ghuav iti, bali ko wit aghorir ingangarim g…®fa. Ez…® Rut uan asamir amebam Naomi ko ikiav…®ra iti.
\c 3
\ms1 Boas arazir aghuim Rut gami
\mr (Sapta 3)
\s1 Naomi Rut bagh patam…®n apighasa
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar man Rut…®n asamim Naomi kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivim n…® oragh, k…® n…® bagh gumazitam…®n apight…® a n…®n ik…®, deragh n…®n gant…® n…® derav…®ra ikiam.
\v 2 Gumazir kam Boas, en ik…®zimra. N…® an ingangarir amiziba ko ingari. N…® oragh, a d…®mangan balin iniba kua dar dagheba isir danganim…®n mang…® ingaram.
\v 3 N…® mang…® ruegh uan mughuriar aghuim zuir borem uab…® daghuigh. Egh korotiar aghuim arugh, egh balin iniba kua dar dagheba isir danganir kam…®n mang…®. N…® mang…® an damazim…®n otivan mark…®, n…® teght…® a mar damegh g…®vaka.
\v 4 Egh a dakus…® mang…®t…® n…® ganigh fogh…®va, g…®n mang…® an suanv…®r…®n an aver inim fegh m…®togh. A g…®n bizir tizim n…® bagh a damus…®, a n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Rut an m…®g…®r…®g…®am ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra damuam.‚Äù
