\v 14 Egha Boas ghaze, ‚ÄúNguibam…®n gumazamiziba foghan mark…®, n…® danganir kam…®n ize.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Rut Boas…®n suanv…®r…®n ir…®ghav ikia ghua am…®nim bar itima a d…®kafi. Ez…® gumazitam an ganizir puvat…®.
\v 15 Ez…® Boas Rut m…®gei, ‚ÄúNir d…®p…®zim…®n itim f…®righ egh m…®tarim…®n m…®n an suiragh.‚Äù Ez…® Rut a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Ez…® Boas balin ov…®ziba an inim gingez…®, dar os…®mt…®zim 20 kilon tu. Ez…® Boas Rut…®n akuragha da isa a gat…®z…®, Rut ada inigha zui. Egha Boas uamategha nguibam…®n ghu.
\s1 Rut bizir otivizibar gun Naomi m…®keme
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Rut ghua d…®penim…®n otoz…® an asamim an azara, ‚ÄúNan guivim kar n…®rara?‚Äù Ez…® Rut Boas a gamizir bizibar gun uan asamim m…®keme.
\p 
\v 17 Egha Rut ghaze, ‚ÄúBoas kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® pura iz…® n…® bativan an aghua. Kamagh…®n a n…® bagha balin ov…®zir av…®riba na gan…®ngi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Naomi ghaze, ‚ÄúNan asamim, n…® tong orarkegh, Boas pura daperagh ikeghan kogham. A bizir kam bagh ingar mang…® anek…®righv…®rama avughsam. Ga pura ik…® ganam bizir tizimra otivam.‚Äù
\c 4
\ms1 God Naomi derav…®ra a gami
\mr (Sapta 4)
\s1 Boas Rut…®n gara an akurvasi
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam Boas ghua nguibam…®n bizibav geir danganim…®n ghugha, aperaghav ikia gara iti. Egha gari Elimelek…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazim izi. Gumazir kam a faragha an gun Rut m…®keme. Ez…® Boas an diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúAveghbuam, n…® kagh iz…® daperagh.‚Äù Ez…® a ghuava apera.
\v 2 Egha Boas nguibam…®n itir gumazir aruar 10pla m…®kemez…® me uaghan iza apiaghav iti.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® a uan ik…®zir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® fo, Naomi Moap…®n kantri ategha uamategha ize. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n en ik…®zim Elimelek nguazir otevim anemangasa.
\v 4 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan ifongiam kamak…®n, n…® bizir kam g…®fogh. K…® n…® m…®gei, n…® nguazir kam gives…® a givesegh. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra en nguibam…®n itir gumazir aruaba ko kagh apiaghav itir gumazamizibar damazim…®n a givesegh. N…® aghuagh m…®k…®mt…® k…® foka. N…®rara guizbang…®ra nan faragha ikia nguazir kam givezamin ingangarim iti, ez…® k…® n…®n g…®n ikia egha uaghan a givezamin ingangarim iti.‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazir kam ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® a givezam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Boas a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Naomin nguazim givezegh, egh uaghan Rut inigh an ikiam. A gumazir aremezim…®n amuir odiarim, Moapian amizim. N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, Rut otaritam bateght…® borir kam uan afeziar aremezim…®n nguazim…®n ik…®t…® men ziam nguazir kam…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® an ik…®zim ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n k…® nguazir kam givezeghan kogham. K…® uan bizibagh n…®ghn…®si. K…® biziba abigh uan boriba ko borir igharaziba sara dan…®ngan aghua. N…® a givesegh k…® aghua.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7-8 \xt God…®n Araziba 25:9\x*Bar fom…®ra Israelia arazir mam iti. Ik…®zim…®n aven me uarira uan nguaziba an…®ga dagh iveza kamagh…®n ami. Gumazir mam uan dagarir asuam suegha mav gan…®di. Israelia arazir kam gamua egha uan akaba ak…®ri.
\v 8 Ez…® gumazir kam Boas m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uab…® nguazir kam givesegh.‚Äù Egha uan dagarir asuam suegha a gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Boas kamagh…®n gumazir aruaba ko maraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n ia bar uan damazibar ganigha fo, Naomi faragha Elimelek, Kilion ko Malon…®n bizibar suira, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® Naomin dafarim…®n bar adagh ivese.
\v 10 Egh uaghan k…® Rut inigh an ikiam, a nan amuim a Moapian amizim. A faragha Malon…®n ikez…® Malon areme. Eght…® Malon…®n nguazir as…®zim an adarazir dafarim…®n ikiam. Eght…® aremezir gumazim, an nguibam…®n iti darazi an ziam g…®n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ikiam. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia uan damazibar bizir k…® amizir kam…®n ganigha a g…®fo.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Jenesis 29:31\x*Ez…® gumazir aruaba ko, me ko itir gumaziba ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra e oregha uan damazibar gani. E kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azangs…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄòGod amizir n…®n d…®penim…®n izamin kam deragh a damu, egh a damight…® a Lea ko Resel…®n m…®n borir av…®riba batam. E fo, aning borir av…®riba batez…® Israel…®n itir adarazir d…®bobonim ghuavanabo. Eght…® n…® uab…® Efratan adarazir aven gumazir ekiam…®n m…®n otogh, Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n aven ziar ekiam iniam.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Jenesis 38:27-30\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God borir av…®riba gua dan…®ngam. Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n adarazir amight…® me Peres…®n adarazir m…®n bar av…®rasemegham, Peres a Juda ko Tamar…®n otarim.‚Äô ‚Äù
\s1 Rut Naomin igiavotarim bate
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Boas Rut inigha an iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God deragha Rut gamiz…®, a navim asegha otarim bate.
\v 14 Ez…® amiziba kamagh…®n Naomi m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe! A igavatarim n…® gan…®ngi. Eght…® igavatarir kam, a n…®n ik…®zim…®n aven akurvazir gumazim…®n ik…®, egh n…®n gan deraghv…®ra n…® damuam. A Israel…®n adarazir aven ziar ekiam iniam.
\v 15 N…®n asamim bar n…® gifongez…®, n…® uaghan bar a gifonge. N…®n asamim bar n…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, n…®n otarir 7pla n…® gifueghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…® otarir kam, a n…®n akurvagh mang…® n…® ghurighamin dughiam a n…®n ganam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Naomi otarim gifuegha uan apozim gat…®gha derav…®rama a gami.
\v 17 Ez…® nguibar kam…®n amiziba ghaze, ‚ÄúNaomi dat…®r…®gh…®n otarim iti.‚Äù
\p Egha me borim ziam, ‚ÄúObet,‚Äù a gat…®. Ez…® g…®n Obet Jesin afeziam…®n oto, ez…® Jesi Devit…®n afeziam…®n oto.
\s1 Atrivim Devit…®n inazir afeziaba
\p 
\v 18 Kar Peres…®n adarazir ghua Devit…®n tu, men ziabar kara: Peres a Hesron…®n afeziam.
\v 19 Ez…® Hesron a Ram…®n afeziam, ez…® Ram a Aminadap…®n afeziam.
\v 20 Ez…® Aminadap a Nason…®n afeziam, ez…® Nason a Salmon…®n afeziam.
\v 21 Ez…® Salmon a Boas…®n afeziam, ez…® Boas a Obet…®n afeziam.
